tfits\", \"from\": 996, \"to\": 1009}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And I am sad to say that there are not any innovations used in the design.\\\"\", \"from\": 1100, \"to\": 1176, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any innovations\", \"from\": 1140, \"to\": 1155}, {\"ngram\": \"the design\", \"from\": 1164, \"to\": 1174}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Red, white and blue have to be part of the American uniform, Sakaki said, but not dominate all of the design.\", \"from\": 1180, \"to\": 1289, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1223, \"end\": 1231, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999999804459, \"rank\": 1.6641603364099523e-11, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1241, \"end\": 1247, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cleyera_japonica\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.425832439160798e-23, \"text\": \"Sakaki\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cleyera_japonica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cleyera_japonica\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 1211, \"to\": 1215}, {\"ngram\": \"the design\", \"from\": 1278, \"to\": 1288}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She added the big, bold lettering and numbers of the uniform take away from the sophistication and elegance of the outfit, rendering it \\\"busy.\\\"\", \"from\": 1290, \"to\": 1433, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the big, bold lettering\", \"from\": 1300, \"to\": 1323}, {\"ngram\": \"numbers\", \"from\": 1328, \"to\": 1335}, {\"ngram\": \"the uniform\", \"from\": 1339, \"to\": 1350}, {\"ngram\": \"the sophistication\", \"from\": 1366, \"to\": 1384}, {\"ngram\": \"elegance\", \"from\": 1389, \"to\": 1397}, {\"ngram\": \"the outfit\", \"from\": 1401, \"to\": 1411}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I would have used some innovative, recyclable materials for some of [the uniforms].\", \"from\": 1435, \"to\": 1519, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some innovative, recyclable materials\", \"from\": 1454, \"to\": 1491}, {\"ngram\": \"the uniforms\", \"from\": 1505, \"to\": 1517}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I would not outfit our 592 athletes in a pair of jeans.\", \"from\": 1520, \"to\": 1575, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our 592 athletes\", \"from\": 1539, \"to\": 1555}, {\"ngram\": \"a pair\", \"from\": 1559, \"to\": 1565}, {\"ngram\": \"jeans\", \"from\": 1569, \"to\": 1574}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yes, jeans are representative of the United States, yet it lacks that sophistication and elegance,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1576, \"to\": 1685, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1613, \"end\": 1626, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999995975486, \"rank\": 4.024750321202921e-10, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"jeans\", \"from\": 1581, \"to\": 1586}, {\"ngram\": \"that sophistication\", \"from\": 1641, \"to\": 1660}, {\"ngram\": \"elegance\", \"from\": 1665, \"to\": 1673}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Since 2008 Ralph Lauren has done a \\\"phenomenal job\\\" clothing American Olympians, but it's now time to give other top-notch fashion designers the opportunity to showcase their talents, she stressed.\", \"from\": 1687, \"to\": 1884, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1698, \"end\": 1710, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren\", \"score\": 0.9999970181851386, \"rank\": 2.98182386244416e-06, \"text\": \"Ralph Lauren\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren\"}, {\"begin\": 1748, \"end\": 1756, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999999804459, \"rank\": 1.66416033640